query:
SELECT 
              id as "id: u32",
              number as "number: u32",
              election_id as "election_id: u32",
              status as "status: _",
              location,
              start_date,
              start_time
            FROM (
              SELECT 
                id, 
                number, 
                election_id, 
                status, 
                location,
                start_date,
                start_time,
              row_number() over (
                PARTITION BY election_id
                ORDER BY number DESC 
              ) AS row_number FROM committee_sessions
            ) t WHERE t.row_number = 1
